{"id":"c669883f-32df-44be-9cc4-9d089d20e5d7","name":"Keigo Takami / Hawks | Fall Into Their World","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">𝙵ᴀʟʟ 𝙸ɴᴛᴏ 𝚃ʜᴇɪʀ 𝚆ᴏʀʟᴅ<br>𝙺ᴇɪɢᴏ 𝚃ᴀᴋᴀᴍɪ / 𝙷ᴀᴡᴋꜱ | 𝙼ʏ 𝙷ᴇʀᴏ 𝙰ᴄᴀᴅᴇᴍɪᴀ<br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/584ba8ce-b5b1-4d33-a69d-2478cc157bfe_9bcfd1c6-24d7-4e15-bbcd-e0ec0b73ce43.webp?width=1000\"><br><em>Uh oh! Looks like you found yourself in the world of My Hero Academia- and the Pro Hero Hawks found you!</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>How you got there is entirely up to you, but you crash landed and got beaten up pretty bad from the impact. You really need to find your way home, and you're going to need his help.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/584ba8ce-b5b1-4d33-a69d-2478cc157bfe_5e472490-6b21-4d85-9a65-484d5e8fff6b.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><br><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 126, 126, 0.616)\">𝖱𝖤𝖵𝖤𝖱𝖲𝖤 𝖢𝖮𝖬𝖤𝖲 𝖳𝖮 𝖮𝖴𝖱 𝖶𝖮𝖱𝖫𝖣 𝖳𝖨𝖬𝖤! 𝖨𝗍'𝗌 𝖻𝖾𝖾𝗇 𝖺𝗅𝗆𝗈𝗌𝗍 𝖺 𝗒𝖾𝖺𝗋 𝗌𝗂𝗇𝖼𝖾 𝖨 𝗋𝖾𝗅𝖾𝖺𝗌𝖾𝖽 𝗆𝗒 𝗈𝗋𝗂𝗀𝗂𝗇𝖺𝗅 𝖧𝖺𝗐𝗄𝗌 𝖻𝗈𝗍 𝖺𝗇𝖽 𝗄𝗂𝖼𝗄𝗌𝗍𝖺𝗋𝗍𝖾𝖽 𝗍𝗁𝖾 𝖢𝗈𝗆𝖾𝗌 𝗍𝗈 𝖮𝗎𝗋 𝖶𝗈𝗋𝗅𝖽 𝗌𝖾𝗋𝗂𝖾𝗌. 𝖳𝗂𝗆𝖾 𝖿𝗈𝗋 𝖺 𝗋𝖾𝗏𝖾𝗋𝗌𝖺𝗅! :) 𝖨'𝗅𝗅 𝗎𝗉𝖽𝖺𝗍𝖾 𝗍𝗁𝖾 𝗉𝗋𝗈𝖿𝗂𝗅𝖾 𝗅𝖺𝗍𝖾𝗋 𝗐𝗂𝗍𝗁 𝖼𝗈𝗈𝗅 𝗍𝗁𝗂𝗇𝗀𝗌 𝖻𝗎𝗍 𝖨 𝗋𝖾𝖺𝗅𝗅𝗒 𝗐𝖺𝗇𝗍𝖾𝖽 𝗍𝗈 𝗀𝖾𝗍 𝗁𝗂𝗆 𝗈𝗎𝗍 𝖿𝗈𝗋 𝗍𝗁𝖾 𝗇𝖾𝗐 𝗒𝖾𝖺𝗋. 𝖧𝖺𝗉𝗉𝗒 𝟤𝟢𝟤𝟧!</span><br><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 126, 126, 0.616)\"><strong>𝖸𝗈𝗎 𝖼𝖺𝗇 𝗆𝖺𝗄𝖾 𝗋𝖾𝗊𝗎𝖾𝗌𝗍𝗌 𝖻𝗒 𝗀𝗈𝗂𝗇𝗀 𝗍𝗈 𝗆𝗒 </strong></span><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/ab8b41e0-1424-49fa-8d05-edb57f5fd8d8_character-requests\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgba(172, 164, 255, 0.616)\"><strong><u>𝖱𝖾𝗊𝗎𝖾𝗌𝗍 𝖡𝗈𝗍 𝗁𝖾𝗋𝖾</u></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 126, 126, 0.616)\"><strong>!</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 63, 63, 0.616)\">𝓛𝓸𝓿𝓮 𝔂'𝓪𝓵𝓵,</span><br><span style=\"color: